[SPEAKER_01] Kako nam mogu ostaviti pečat za život?

444
00:39:40,519 --> 00:39:44,840
[SPEAKER_00] Pa oni nam već svojom prisutnošću ostavljaju pečat za život.

445
00:39:44,840 --> 00:39:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi u onoj primarnoj dobi mi neverbalno komuniciramo.

446
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:56,400
[SPEAKER_00] Znači već to energija, na kraju je energija koju mi dobivamo već u maminom trbuhu.

447
00:39:56,400 --> 00:40:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, u trbuhu se već događa prvi izraz ljubavi koje mi doživljavamo,

448
00:40:03,980 --> 00:40:07,039
[SPEAKER_00] a to je kroz pupčanu vrpcu i kroz hranjenje.

449
00:40:07,039 --> 00:40:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] To za nas je već jedna vrsta pod navodnicima programiranja što za nas znači ljubav.

450
00:40:13,119 --> 00:40:15,659
[SPEAKER_00] Znači neko nam daje hranu za život.

451
00:40:15,659 --> 00:40:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] I onda se rodimo, male smo bebe i tada zapravo upijamo energiju naših roditelja,

452
00:40:23,679 --> 00:40:26,679
[SPEAKER_00] onih s kojima najviše vremena provodimo.

453
00:40:26,679 --> 00:40:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kreću nekakva usmjeravanja.

454
00:40:30,199 --> 00:40:34,099
[SPEAKER_00] Kada dijete sa neke tri godine počinje zapravo doživljavati svijet,

455
00:40:34,099 --> 00:40:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] primjećuje odnose, aha, znači ovo je ovako, ovo je onako.

456
00:40:38,079 --> 00:40:40,519
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, evo, počne nekako otvarati oči.

457
00:40:40,519 --> 00:40:45,440
[SPEAKER_00] Kreću i ta nekakva usmjeravanja naših roditelja

458
00:40:45,440 --> 00:40:50,099
[SPEAKER_00] prema, kako bi rekla, otisku onog što su oni primili

459
00:40:50,099 --> 00:40:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] i što oni jedino znaju i što oni misle da je za nas dobro.

460
00:40:54,480 --> 00:40:56,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je upravo glavna stvar.

461
00:40:56,739 --> 00:41:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] Što oni misle da je za nas dobro.

462
00:41:00,059 --> 00:41:01,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to ne znači to.

463
00:41:01,820 --> 00:41:04,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to ne znači da je to zaista za nas dobro.

464
00:41:04,880 --> 00:41:08,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ali oni nam žele najbolje.

465
00:41:08,280 --> 00:41:13,179
[SPEAKER_00] A vrlo često se dogodi da baš ne ode u smjeru onoga što mi zaista jesmo.

466
00:41:14,619 --> 00:41:21,440
[SPEAKER_00] I tu se onda događaju ti naši momenti, možda nekakve neravnoteže ili nelagode,

467
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] sami sa sobom, koji od nas traže buđenje.

468
00:41:25,059 --> 00:41:30,420
[SPEAKER_00] Koji od nas traže učenje kako sebe uopće upoznati.

469
00:41:30,420 --> 00:41:34,360
[SPEAKER_00] Kako uopće shvatiti ko sam ja i što želim.

470
00:41:34,360 --> 00:41:42,840
[SPEAKER_00] I ima još nešto, a to je nas jako uvjetuju naša uvjerenja.

471
00:41:42,840 --> 00:41:44,500
[SPEAKER_00] Objasnite mi to.

472
00:41:44,500 --> 00:41:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] Jako nas ukalupljuju.

473
00:41:46,079 --> 00:41:50,980
[SPEAKER_00] Imala sam nedavno jedan primjer jednog gospodina

474
00:41:50,980 --> 00:41:55,219
[SPEAKER_00] koji ima nekakve obiteljske dinamike,

475
00:41:55,219 --> 00:41:57,739
[SPEAKER_00] neku konstelaciju obiteljsku, događaje razne.

476
00:41:57,739 --> 00:42:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] I prepričava mi tu situaciju i kaže

477
00:42:01,619 --> 00:42:04,480
[SPEAKER_00] šta sam ja zapravo u tom času mogao?

478
00:42:04,480 --> 00:42:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam mogao ili ovo, ili ono.

479
00:42:07,500 --> 00:42:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] I sad ja nasuprod njega, slušajući ga,

480
00:42:10,980 --> 00:42:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] ja kažem, ajde sekundu, samo da ja ti kažem svoje mišljenje.

481
00:42:16,219 --> 00:42:20,739
[SPEAKER_00] Vidiš, ja na primjer, kao neko nepristran u tvojoj koži,

482
00:42:20,739 --> 00:42:23,579
[SPEAKER_00] bi vidjela barem 50 mogućnosti.

483
00:42:23,579 --> 00:42:27,739
[SPEAKER_00] A ti si sebe ograničio na te dvije.

484
00:42:27,739 --> 00:42:32,400
[SPEAKER_00] Jer to su tvoja uvjerenja koja kreiraju tvoj svijet.

485
00:42:32,400 --> 00:42:37,360
[SPEAKER_00] Tu si sebe apsolutno, totalno ograničio

486
00:42:37,360 --> 00:42:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] i uvjetovao na A ili B opciju.

487
00:42:40,380 --> 00:42:45,360
[SPEAKER_00] Da si dopustiš razumijeti i vidjeti

488
00:42:45,360 --> 00:42:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] da su nama stalno dostupne sve mogućnosti,

489
00:42:49,679 --> 00:42:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] a jedino nas od toga dijeli naš um

490
00:42:52,119 --> 00:42:58,679
[SPEAKER_00] koji, kako bi rekla, drži se tih uvjerenja,

491
00:42:58,679 --> 00:43:03,940
[SPEAKER_00] mi bi mogli kompletno otvoriti priču u drugom smjeru.

492
00:43:03,940 --> 00:43:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] Naš život bi u jednoj sekundi mogao izgledati potpuno drugače.

493
00:43:07,099 --> 00:43:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tako će mi moli vas konkretan primjer.

494
00:43:08,960 --> 00:43:10,239
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ga.

495
00:43:10,239 --> 00:43:13,500
[SPEAKER_00] Na primjer, bio mi je jedan gospodin, malo stariji,

496
00:43:13,500 --> 00:43:16,860
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da je imao nekih 70-75 godina.

497
00:43:17,719 --> 00:43:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] Došao je sa stravičnim išijasom,

498
00:43:20,159 --> 00:43:21,900
[SPEAKER_00] ali on je bio cijeli pogrbljen.

499
00:43:21,900 --> 00:43:23,139
[SPEAKER_00] On je jedva ušao.

500
00:43:23,139 --> 00:43:26,719
[SPEAKER_00] On si nije mogao naći mjesto kako bi se sjeo,

501
00:43:26,719 --> 00:43:29,800
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi uopće započeo razgovor,

502
00:43:29,800 --> 00:43:31,260
[SPEAKER_00] da se imalo opusti.

503
00:43:32,119 --> 00:43:38,440
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo nakon 20 minuta nekakvog razgovora samo pričali o njegovim uvjerenjima.

504
00:43:38,440 --> 00:43:43,719
[SPEAKER_00] O tome što je njega toliko zgrčilo i toliko stisnulo.

505
00:43:43,719 --> 00:43:44,260
[SPEAKER_00] Što?

506
00:43:44,260 --> 00:43:48,519
[SPEAKER_00] To su bila nekakva njegova jako kruta uvjerenja.

507
00:43:48,519 --> 00:43:52,519
[SPEAKER_00] Nekakva njegova mišljenja da bi nešto moralo biti točno ovako,

508
00:43:52,519 --> 00:43:53,219
[SPEAKER_00] točno onako.

509
00:43:53,219 --> 00:43:56,739
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, bez ikakvih odstupanja, bez ikakvih dozvoljavanja

510
00:43:56,739 --> 00:44:00,420
[SPEAKER_00] da prilike mogu biti drugačije, da su ljudi drugačiji.

511
00:44:00,420 --> 00:44:03,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, on se drža od toga, kako bi im u narodu rekli,

512
00:44:03,519 --> 00:44:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] kopijan plota.

513
00:44:04,559 --> 00:44:07,639
[SPEAKER_00] Njegovo tijelo je to zaključalo.

514
00:44:07,639 --> 00:44:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] Mi kad smo dosegli ta uvjerenja,

515
00:44:12,119 --> 00:44:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] čovjek se digao kao četvrogodišnje djete.

516
00:44:16,440 --> 00:44:19,420
[SPEAKER_00] Samo što nije skočio sa tog kauča.

517
00:44:19,420 --> 00:44:23,760
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, njegovo tijelo je kroz spoznaju,

518
00:44:24,260 --> 00:44:28,219
[SPEAKER_00] kroz svijest o toj situaciji u razgovoru,

519
00:44:28,219 --> 00:44:30,519
[SPEAKER_00] kroz biokemijski proces,

520
00:44:30,519 --> 00:44:33,320
[SPEAKER_00] kada se dogodi to osvještavanje,

521
00:44:33,320 --> 00:44:36,920
[SPEAKER_00] u našem tijelu biokemija odmah reagira.

522
00:44:36,920 --> 00:44:40,719
[SPEAKER_00] U tom trenutku se tijelo ovako otpustilo.

523
00:44:40,719 --> 00:44:44,099
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek se digao i ja kažem,

524
00:44:44,099 --> 00:44:45,679
[SPEAKER_00] pa jeste svjesni kao?

525
00:44:45,679 --> 00:44:47,280
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže, pa ne mogu vjerojat.

526
00:44:47,280 --> 00:44:52,280
[SPEAKER_00] On nije mi primijetio koliko se ustao i otišao mekši.

527
00:44:52,280 --> 00:44:53,760
[SPEAKER_00] Otišao je kao dječačić.

528
00:44:54,260 --> 00:44:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] Zbog uvjerenja.

529
00:44:55,460 --> 00:45:00,719
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, sabija sebe, ali s time sabija i druge,

530
00:45:00,719 --> 00:45:03,260
[SPEAKER_01] jer na kraju kreva to od drugih očekuje.

531
00:45:03,260 --> 00:45:03,719
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

532
00:45:03,719 --> 00:45:06,300
[SPEAKER_01] Dajte mi još par takvih nekakvih primjera

533
00:45:06,300 --> 00:45:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] kroz naše svakodnevne živote.

534
00:45:09,179 --> 00:45:13,800
[SPEAKER_01] Rekli ste, ne znam, dosta ljudi ne spava dobro.

535
00:45:13,800 --> 00:45:16,380
[SPEAKER_01] Hajde, što još.

536
00:45:16,380 --> 00:45:17,559
[SPEAKER_01] Onda dosta ih je dobro.

537
00:45:17,559 --> 00:45:22,659
[SPEAKER_01] Spomenuli ste melankoliju, ali dosta ih je apatično danas.

538
00:45:22,659 --> 00:45:25,219
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ja ću sad to, pa možete se još nešto sjetim.

539
00:45:25,280 --> 00:45:26,980
[SPEAKER_00] Pa evo, sjetila sam se sad recimo...

540
00:45:26,980 --> 00:45:28,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ne idem ništa po pitanjima.

541
00:45:28,360 --> 00:45:29,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ma i nije ni bitno.

542
00:45:29,539 --> 00:45:32,840
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetila sam se jednog primjera jedne mame,

543
00:45:32,840 --> 00:45:34,760
[SPEAKER_00] moje redovne stranke,

544
00:45:34,760 --> 00:45:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] koja je dobila takav poklon u obliku svog djeteta,

545
00:45:40,119 --> 00:45:41,840
[SPEAKER_00] koja je toliko čudesno,

546
00:45:41,840 --> 00:45:43,820
[SPEAKER_00] toliko zanimljivo,

547
00:45:43,820 --> 00:45:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] toliko otvoreno.

548
00:45:45,539 --> 00:45:47,719
[SPEAKER_00] Potpuno je jedna nova generacija,

549
00:45:47,719 --> 00:45:50,239
[SPEAKER_00] koja je došla nas učit ovdje.

550
00:45:50,239 --> 00:45:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] Koja je došla neopterečena,

551
00:45:53,500 --> 00:45:56,480
[SPEAKER_00] bez onog osjećaja ja moram.

552
00:45:56,480 --> 00:45:59,360
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo ipak još jedan,

553
00:45:59,360 --> 00:46:02,340
[SPEAKER_00] taj stari tip generacija,

554
00:46:02,340 --> 00:46:05,019
[SPEAKER_00] gdje smo mi stalno bili usmjeravani kroz moranja.

555
00:46:05,019 --> 00:46:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je svijet, ova transformacija svijesti,

556
00:46:08,000 --> 00:46:09,840
[SPEAKER_00] sve što proživljavamo zadnjih godina,

557
00:46:09,840 --> 00:46:15,019
[SPEAKER_00] ide upravo u taj najveći iskorak iz tog moram u želim.

558
00:46:15,539 --> 00:46:17,860
[SPEAKER_00] Mi se učimo što zapravo želim.

559
00:46:17,860 --> 00:46:20,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ovo moranje me je naučilo

560
00:46:20,139 --> 00:46:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] da je to totalno izvan svih zakona prirode

561
00:46:25,019 --> 00:46:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] mene i mog tijela.

562
00:46:26,420 --> 00:46:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] I sada takva mama,

563
00:46:28,960 --> 00:46:33,219
[SPEAKER_00] koja je iz te, ajmo reći, generacije moranja,

564
00:46:33,219 --> 00:46:35,400
[SPEAKER_00] dobi djete slobodnjaka.

565
00:46:35,400 --> 00:46:38,840
[SPEAKER_00] Djete koje malo, ajmo rećiš,

566
00:46:38,840 --> 00:46:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] pod navodnicima lebdi,

567
00:46:40,159 --> 00:46:43,079
[SPEAKER_00] ona ga mora stalno spuštat na zemlju,

568
00:46:43,079 --> 00:46:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] jer ipak ima školu,

569
00:46:44,300 --> 00:46:46,179
[SPEAKER_00] pa ima obaveze i ostalo,

570
00:46:46,179 --> 00:46:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali ona nikako,

571
00:46:48,119 --> 00:46:51,519
[SPEAKER_00] ni na koji način ne može prihvatiti to svoje djete.

572
00:46:51,519 --> 00:46:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je u takvim unutarnjim sukobima.

573
00:46:54,559 --> 00:46:57,179
[SPEAKER_00] To su takvi napadi bijesa

574
00:46:57,179 --> 00:46:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] u našim razgovorima.

575
00:46:58,619 --> 00:47:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ona zaista se tako čvrsto drži toga.

576
00:47:03,340 --> 00:47:05,579
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, njen cijeli sistema,

577
00:47:05,579 --> 00:47:06,559
[SPEAKER_00] majmo reći iznutra,

578
00:47:06,559 --> 00:47:07,820
[SPEAKER_00] puca po šabovima,

579
00:47:07,820 --> 00:47:11,019
[SPEAKER_00] jer ona to djete ne može savladat,

580
00:47:11,019 --> 00:47:12,639
[SPEAKER_00] ali to djete je nesavladljivo

581
00:47:12,639 --> 00:47:15,219
[SPEAKER_00] i ono ju uči tome.

582
00:47:15,219 --> 00:47:18,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ona nije spremna prihvatiti to učenje.

583
00:47:18,500 --> 00:47:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ona nije spremna se prilagoditi

584
00:47:21,340 --> 00:47:24,659
[SPEAKER_00] i možda početi primjenjivati neki drugi jezik

585
00:47:24,659 --> 00:47:26,719
[SPEAKER_00] ili drugi pristup prema tome djetetu.

586
00:47:26,800 --> 00:47:27,920
[SPEAKER_00] Može li se to?

587
00:47:27,920 --> 00:47:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] Može se.

588
00:47:28,960 --> 00:47:30,260
[SPEAKER_00] Apsolutno se može.

589
00:47:30,260 --> 00:47:32,519
[SPEAKER_00] Snagom karaktera može se što šta?

590
00:47:32,519 --> 00:47:33,119
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

591
00:47:33,119 --> 00:47:35,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kroz to dozvoljavanje,

592
00:47:35,059 --> 00:47:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] kroz to dopustim da je moje djete

593
00:47:37,880 --> 00:47:39,480
[SPEAKER_00] tako kako je.

594
00:47:39,480 --> 00:47:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] Da je moje djete došlo ovdje meni

595
00:47:42,059 --> 00:47:42,900
[SPEAKER_00] kao primjer,

596
00:47:42,900 --> 00:47:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] da je moje djete meni prilika za moj rast.

597
00:47:45,539 --> 00:47:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] Mi imamo stalno priliku za rast.

598
00:47:48,159 --> 00:47:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Stalo imamo priliku za promjenu.

599
00:47:50,000 --> 00:47:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko puta mi to prihvatimo?

600
00:47:52,119 --> 00:47:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] E to je sad druga priča.

601
00:47:53,920 --> 00:47:55,360
[SPEAKER_00] To je sad naša stvar.

602
00:47:55,420 --> 00:47:56,980
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ću ja opet dajte primjere.

603
00:47:56,980 --> 00:48:00,219
[SPEAKER_00] Pa primjer je.

604
00:48:00,219 --> 00:48:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] Evo nekakvi glavobolja.

605
00:48:01,519 --> 00:48:03,420
[SPEAKER_00] Naprimjer, to je često.

606
00:48:03,420 --> 00:48:05,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kao iridolog,

607
00:48:05,719 --> 00:48:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] nekako promatram šarenicu oka.

608
00:48:09,059 --> 00:48:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ja u šarenici oka odmah vidim

609
00:48:12,199 --> 00:48:14,980
[SPEAKER_00] ako je nekakva fiziološka pozadina

610
00:48:14,980 --> 00:48:17,400
[SPEAKER_00] ili ako je nekakva hormonalna pozadina

611
00:48:17,400 --> 00:48:21,139
[SPEAKER_00] kad mi se stranka žali na probleme

612
00:48:21,139 --> 00:48:23,599
[SPEAKER_00] glavobolja ili migrena.

613
00:48:24,739 --> 00:48:25,820
[SPEAKER_00] na oko pokazuje

614
00:48:25,820 --> 00:48:27,760
[SPEAKER_00] apsolutno čistu sliku.

615
00:48:27,760 --> 00:48:29,179
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

616
00:48:29,179 --> 00:48:32,340
[SPEAKER_00] apsolutno nikakve veze nema

617
00:48:32,340 --> 00:48:34,840
[SPEAKER_00] sa bilošćim fizičkim ili fiziološkim

618
00:48:34,840 --> 00:48:37,159
[SPEAKER_00] nego isključivo sa nečim.

619
00:48:37,159 --> 00:48:38,840
[SPEAKER_00] Najčešće je to povezano

620
00:48:38,840 --> 00:48:40,219
[SPEAKER_00] sa deficitom želuca

621
00:48:40,219 --> 00:48:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] i želučane kiseline.

622
00:48:41,619 --> 00:48:43,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet se vraćamo

623
00:48:43,780 --> 00:48:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] kod toga što mogu probaviti

624
00:48:46,059 --> 00:48:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] ili prihvatiti ili ne prihvatiti.

625
00:48:48,539 --> 00:48:52,260
[SPEAKER_01] Čekajte, želite reći da su okidači za glavobolje

626
00:48:52,260 --> 00:48:56,400
[SPEAKER_01] i migrene nekakva neprihvaćanja nečega, nekoga.

627
00:48:56,599 --> 00:48:58,780
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, opet ti kruti čvrsti stavovi.

628
00:48:58,780 --> 00:49:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] I opet kroz recimo prehranu

629
00:49:04,039 --> 00:49:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] koja je vrlo nježna za želudac

630
00:49:07,199 --> 00:49:08,340
[SPEAKER_00] i podržavajuća

631
00:49:08,340 --> 00:49:10,619
[SPEAKER_00] uz određenu biljnu terapiju,

632
00:49:10,619 --> 00:49:13,019
[SPEAKER_00] uz određene vježbe disanja,

633
00:49:13,019 --> 00:49:16,820
[SPEAKER_00] mi poznajemo jako puno različitih vježba disanja

634
00:49:16,820 --> 00:49:19,920
[SPEAKER_00] i zaista su nam predivan alat

635
00:49:19,920 --> 00:49:25,619
[SPEAKER_00] koji nas jako dobro zna posložiti.

636
00:49:25,619 --> 00:49:30,679
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, uz sve to mi uredimo želudac

637
00:49:30,679 --> 00:49:33,400
[SPEAKER_00] uz, na primjer, bahove kapi

638
00:49:33,400 --> 00:49:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] koje dijeluju na naše emotivno tijelo

639
00:49:36,039 --> 00:49:37,940
[SPEAKER_00] na najsubtilniji način.

640
00:49:37,940 --> 00:49:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, doslovno prepoznaju

641
00:49:40,039 --> 00:49:43,940
[SPEAKER_00] onu točku spajanja nas sa prirodom.

642
00:49:44,420 --> 00:49:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] esencija iz prirode balansira naše emocije.

643
00:49:48,480 --> 00:49:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] Te glavo bolje nestanu.

644
00:49:50,440 --> 00:49:51,739
[SPEAKER_00] Imam takav primjer.

645
00:49:51,739 --> 00:49:53,280
[SPEAKER_00] Jedne stranke baš u Sloveniji.

646
00:49:53,280 --> 00:49:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ona više ne zna što su glavo bolje.

647
00:49:57,000 --> 00:50:00,739
[SPEAKER_00] Jer smo radili na svim tim segmentima nje.

648
00:50:00,739 --> 00:50:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] I što se pokazalo?

649
00:50:02,539 --> 00:50:04,880
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, što je nju najviše?

650
00:50:04,880 --> 00:50:07,900
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, koji je osjećaj to?

651
00:50:07,900 --> 00:50:10,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kod te stranke se konkretno radilo o tome

652
00:50:10,800 --> 00:50:13,159
[SPEAKER_00] da je imala jedan primjer

653
00:50:13,159 --> 00:50:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo strogog djetinstva.

654
00:50:16,219 --> 00:50:19,280
[SPEAKER_00] Konkretnije, majka je bila primjer

655
00:50:19,280 --> 00:50:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] koja joj doslovno, kako bi rekla,

656
00:50:22,860 --> 00:50:24,300
[SPEAKER_00] nije ju prihvaćala

657
00:50:24,300 --> 00:50:26,679
[SPEAKER_00] i bila je jako kruta i stroga sa njom.

658
00:50:26,679 --> 00:50:29,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je taj princip ponašanja

659
00:50:29,340 --> 00:50:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] preuzela na sebe.

660
00:50:31,019 --> 00:50:33,199
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je sebe jako zakinula,

661
00:50:33,199 --> 00:50:34,639
[SPEAKER_00] zaštetila i blokirala.

662
00:50:34,639 --> 00:50:36,820
[SPEAKER_00] I tu smo opet kod tog,

663
00:50:36,820 --> 00:50:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je važno da smo mi protočni.

664
00:50:38,659 --> 00:50:40,219
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi bili zdravi,

665
00:50:40,219 --> 00:50:42,219
[SPEAKER_00] mi trebamo biti protočni.

666
00:50:42,219 --> 00:50:45,340
[SPEAKER_00] A naše prirodno stanje je da smo zdravi.

667
00:50:45,340 --> 00:50:47,420
[SPEAKER_00] I o tom se isto premalo priča

668
00:50:47,420 --> 00:50:48,340
[SPEAKER_00] o ovom društvu.

669
00:50:48,340 --> 00:50:50,139
[SPEAKER_00] Imala sam jedan zanimljiv primjer.

670
00:50:50,139 --> 00:50:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] Imala sam kod kuće nekakve radove.

671
00:50:52,440 --> 00:50:55,280
[SPEAKER_00] Imala sam jednog mladog majstora

672
00:50:55,280 --> 00:50:57,059
[SPEAKER_00] koje je cijeli dan proveo kod mene.

673
00:50:57,059 --> 00:50:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam ga stalno s nečim nudila.

674
00:50:58,539 --> 00:51:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] Da li će nešto popit, pojesti.

675
00:51:00,119 --> 00:51:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, ne, ne, ne.

676
00:51:01,059 --> 00:51:03,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ja si volim sam skuhat na kraju dana

677
00:51:03,679 --> 00:51:04,699
[SPEAKER_00] kad ja dođem doma.

678
00:51:04,699 --> 00:51:05,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ja jedem zdravu hranu.

679
00:51:05,840 --> 00:51:07,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ja si sam to sve nabavljam.

680
00:51:07,679 --> 00:51:08,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem krasno.

681
00:51:08,780 --> 00:51:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] A mlađi je čovjek.

682
00:51:10,000 --> 00:51:12,260
[SPEAKER_00] Imao on tipa 25-26 godina.

683
00:51:12,260 --> 00:51:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] Nije znao s čim se ja bavim.

684
00:51:14,420 --> 00:51:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] Uopće o tome nije bilo riječi.

685
00:51:16,739 --> 00:51:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] I on kaže, znate, ja sam vam se nedavno preselio

686
00:51:19,119 --> 00:51:21,159
[SPEAKER_00] iz jednog manje grada.

687
00:51:21,159 --> 00:51:22,300
[SPEAKER_00] Je došao živjeti u Zagreb

688
00:51:22,300 --> 00:51:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] i preselio i karton zdravstveni

689
00:51:24,500 --> 00:51:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] kod lječnika primarne prakse.

690
00:51:26,460 --> 00:51:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] I došao je s praznim kartonom.

691
00:51:28,539 --> 00:51:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] I lječnica primarne prakse je otvorila karton

692
00:51:31,599 --> 00:51:35,480
[SPEAKER_00] i rekla mu u čudu, pa vaš karton je prazan.

693
00:51:35,480 --> 00:51:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] I on je rekao, pa da, pa ja vam u životu nisam bio bolestan.

694
00:51:39,599 --> 00:51:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je bila u šoku.

695
00:51:41,079 --> 00:51:42,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je ponavljala za redom.

696
00:51:42,860 --> 00:51:44,519
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kako je to moguće?

697
00:51:44,800 --> 00:51:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] Kao da sa njim postoji nekakva greška.

698
00:51:46,820 --> 00:51:48,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ma čekajte, kako je moguće

699
00:51:48,800 --> 00:51:50,840
[SPEAKER_00] da bi nikad niste bili bolesni?

700
00:51:50,840 --> 00:51:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ma je li to moguće?

701
00:51:52,380 --> 00:51:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ne.

702
00:51:52,980 --> 00:51:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ona se načuđavala.

703
00:51:54,960 --> 00:51:57,360
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je baš ostalo ovako

704
00:51:57,360 --> 00:52:00,320
[SPEAKER_00] jedna zgodna pod navodnicima anegdota.

705
00:52:00,320 --> 00:52:03,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ali da, prirodno stanje je da smo bolesni.

706
00:52:03,099 --> 00:52:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] Da smo zdravi.

707
00:52:04,460 --> 00:52:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] Isprečavaju se, naravno, da smo zdravi.

708
00:52:06,980 --> 00:52:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] A tijelo nam pokazuje neku neravnotežu

709
00:52:11,039 --> 00:52:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] koja onda vodi prema bolesti

710
00:52:13,539 --> 00:52:15,199
[SPEAKER_00] ako je dugo zanemarujemo.

711
00:52:15,199 --> 00:52:17,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ne poštujemo

712
00:52:17,699 --> 00:52:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ne reagiramo

713
00:52:19,000 --> 00:52:21,119
[SPEAKER_00] kod tih nekakvih neravnoteža,

714
00:52:21,119 --> 00:52:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] ne uputimo se na pravo mjesto,

715
00:52:24,380 --> 00:52:26,340
[SPEAKER_00] ne potražimo savjet ili pomoć,

716
00:52:26,340 --> 00:52:28,920
[SPEAKER_00] onda postaju malo ipak kroničnije.

717
00:52:28,920 --> 00:52:30,619
[SPEAKER_00] Isto je nekakve akutne faze

718
00:52:30,619 --> 00:52:33,280
[SPEAKER_00] voli prijeću u kroničnu fazu.

719
00:52:33,400 --> 00:52:36,179
[SPEAKER_01] To znači zapravo da, kako ste rekli,

720
00:52:36,179 --> 00:52:37,820
[SPEAKER_01] tijelo nam šalje signale.

721
00:52:37,820 --> 00:52:40,480
[SPEAKER_01] Male, pa možda malo veće.

722
00:52:40,480 --> 00:52:42,639
[SPEAKER_01] I trebamo ih znati, prepoznati,

723
00:52:42,639 --> 00:52:45,920
[SPEAKER_01] a ne odmah juriti i piti nekakve kemije,

724
00:52:45,920 --> 00:52:47,960
[SPEAKER_01] nego uroniti u sebe same.

725
00:52:48,179 --> 00:52:49,239
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, tako je.

726
00:52:49,239 --> 00:52:51,340
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajte, puno ljudi, ne znam,

727
00:52:51,340 --> 00:52:53,480
[SPEAKER_00] iz nekakvog trenda voli trčati,

728
00:52:53,480 --> 00:52:55,119
[SPEAKER_00] puno je tih škola trčanja,

729
00:52:55,119 --> 00:52:57,719
[SPEAKER_00] puno je raznih tih polumaratona, maratona.

730
00:52:57,719 --> 00:52:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je krasan sport.

731
00:52:59,039 --> 00:53:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet, mi smo,

732
00:53:01,460 --> 00:53:05,320
[SPEAKER_00] svako za sebe individua je drugačija.

733
00:53:05,320 --> 00:53:07,139
[SPEAKER_00] Vi sad pogledajte u toj jednoj skupini

734
00:53:07,139 --> 00:53:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] nekakvih tih natjecatelja u trčanju.

735
00:53:09,500 --> 00:53:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je raznih tipova.

736
00:53:10,940 --> 00:53:12,719
[SPEAKER_00] Već ako pričamo o ovim tipovima

737
00:53:12,719 --> 00:53:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] iz kineske medicine.

738
00:53:13,940 --> 00:53:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne znam baš da li za svakog dobro

739
00:53:16,760 --> 00:53:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] opterečivat koljena kralježnicu

740
00:53:20,900 --> 00:53:22,639
[SPEAKER_00] s obzirom na njegovu težinu.

741
00:53:22,639 --> 00:53:26,139
[SPEAKER_00] Opterečivat srce s obzirom na njegov srčani deficit.

742
00:53:26,139 --> 00:53:30,340
[SPEAKER_00] Tu se ljudi vole prenaglit

743
00:53:30,340 --> 00:53:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] i ne poslušaju često tijelo

744
00:53:32,960 --> 00:53:37,360
[SPEAKER_00] kada im možda krene nekakvo preskakivanje srca.

745
00:53:37,360 --> 00:53:38,099
[SPEAKER_00] Aritmije.

746
00:53:38,099 --> 00:53:39,639
[SPEAKER_00] Aritmije, recimo, razne.

747
00:53:39,639 --> 00:53:42,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ili nekakvo pojačano znojenje.

748
00:53:42,360 --> 00:53:44,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ili da se uopće ne znoje.

749
00:53:44,039 --> 00:53:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, ja u mom radu jako tome pridodajem

750
00:53:47,539 --> 00:53:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] isto pažnju.

751
00:53:48,440 --> 00:53:51,500
[SPEAKER_00] Baš na tom da to izmjeni tekućina

752
00:53:51,500 --> 00:53:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] u našem tijelu.

753
00:53:52,440 --> 00:53:55,860
[SPEAKER_00] I da li, sukladno tome koliko mi unesemo tekućine,

754
00:53:55,860 --> 00:53:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] da li zapravo naše tijelo

755
00:53:57,840 --> 00:54:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] toliko tekućine i proradi.

756
00:54:00,119 --> 00:54:02,119
[SPEAKER_00] Neki ljudi piju,

757
00:54:02,179 --> 00:54:03,519
[SPEAKER_00] imam primjer jedne osobe

758
00:54:03,519 --> 00:54:05,739
[SPEAKER_00] koja popije po 5-7 litara

759
00:54:05,739 --> 00:54:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] na dan vode

760
00:54:07,380 --> 00:54:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] i stalno

761
00:54:09,440 --> 00:54:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] osjeća željč.

762
00:54:10,940 --> 00:54:12,219
[SPEAKER_00] A u čemu je problem?

763
00:54:12,219 --> 00:54:14,760
[SPEAKER_00] Pa gledajte, razni su problemi,

764
00:54:14,760 --> 00:54:17,639
[SPEAKER_00] ali definitivno se treba usmjeriti

765
00:54:17,639 --> 00:54:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] na bubrežni meridijan,

766
00:54:18,980 --> 00:54:21,039
[SPEAKER_00] kako volimo reći po kineskoj medicini,

767
00:54:22,219 --> 00:54:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] gdje ne radi pravilno ta naša pumpa,

768
00:54:25,000 --> 00:54:26,099
[SPEAKER_00] ta naša izmjena.

769
00:54:26,099 --> 00:54:30,280
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, natri nam je kao element,

770
00:54:30,280 --> 00:54:32,119
[SPEAKER_00] kao mineral važan.

771
00:54:32,119 --> 00:54:35,420
[SPEAKER_00] Tu trebamo vrlo dobro i pažljivo korigirati

772
00:54:35,420 --> 00:54:36,559
[SPEAKER_00] taj natri u tijelu,

773
00:54:36,559 --> 00:54:38,639
[SPEAKER_00] da se uopće javi

774
00:54:38,639 --> 00:54:42,800
[SPEAKER_00] pravilna potreba za žeđi.

775
00:54:42,800 --> 00:54:44,480
[SPEAKER_00] Kao i u gladi.

776
00:54:44,480 --> 00:54:46,420
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo taj hormon leptin

777
00:54:46,420 --> 00:54:47,860
[SPEAKER_00] koji korigira,

778
00:54:47,860 --> 00:54:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno nas upozori,

779
00:54:50,199 --> 00:54:51,300
[SPEAKER_00] evo gladna sam.

780
00:54:51,300 --> 00:54:53,179
[SPEAKER_00] A u stvari možda nisam.

781
00:54:53,179 --> 00:54:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] Možda nisam, da.

782
00:54:54,480 --> 00:54:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] Imate jako puno ljudi,

783
00:54:56,199 --> 00:54:57,199
[SPEAKER_00] imam takvih primjera,

784
00:54:57,739 --> 00:54:58,219
[SPEAKER_00] koji kažu,

785
00:54:58,219 --> 00:55:00,260
[SPEAKER_00] pa ja mogu cijeli dan jest,

786
00:55:00,260 --> 00:55:01,659
[SPEAKER_00] a i ne moram jest,

787
00:55:01,659 --> 00:55:03,059
[SPEAKER_00] ja uopće ne razumijem

788
00:55:03,059 --> 00:55:04,340
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam ja gladan,

789
00:55:04,340 --> 00:55:06,440
[SPEAKER_00] meni kad je hrana pod nosom,

790
00:55:06,440 --> 00:55:07,340
[SPEAKER_00] ja pojedem,

791
00:55:07,340 --> 00:55:09,099
[SPEAKER_00] a onda se uopće ne sjetim.

792
00:55:09,099 --> 00:55:10,219
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, taj hormon

793
00:55:10,219 --> 00:55:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] totalno nije u balansu,

794
00:55:13,480 --> 00:55:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno ne daje pravi impuls

795
00:55:15,559 --> 00:55:16,619
[SPEAKER_00] u pravom trenutku.

796
00:55:16,619 --> 00:55:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] I takve osobe se hrane,

797
00:55:19,460 --> 00:55:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] neću reći ni iz primarnih potreba,

798
00:55:21,880 --> 00:55:23,260
[SPEAKER_00] nego jednostavno očima.

799
00:55:23,260 --> 00:55:23,940
[SPEAKER_00] Jel?

800
00:55:23,940 --> 00:55:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se ono kaže,

801
00:55:25,960 --> 00:55:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] veće su im oči,

802
00:55:27,119 --> 00:55:29,280
[SPEAKER_00] a sa druge strane,

803
00:55:29,280 --> 00:55:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] su jako tu odvojani od sebe.

804
00:55:31,199 --> 00:55:32,659
[SPEAKER_01] Razumijete?

805
00:55:32,659 --> 00:55:33,260
[SPEAKER_01] Kako to mislite?

806
00:55:33,260 --> 00:55:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, ako sve naše fizičke tegobe

807
00:55:37,519 --> 00:55:39,119
[SPEAKER_00] nastaju iz onog nevidljivog,

808
00:55:39,119 --> 00:55:41,119
[SPEAKER_00] što ste rekli na početku,

809
00:55:41,119 --> 00:55:44,659
[SPEAKER_00] znači iz tog nekog mislenog dijela nas

810
00:55:44,659 --> 00:55:47,420
[SPEAKER_00] i zanim sljede emotivnog dijela nas,

811
00:55:47,420 --> 00:55:50,679
[SPEAKER_00] tako treba promatrati tijelo,

812
00:55:50,679 --> 00:55:52,099
[SPEAKER_00] što ono nama poručuje.

813
00:55:52,099 --> 00:55:53,079
[SPEAKER_00] To su moja pitanja

814
00:55:53,079 --> 00:55:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] koja postavljam strankama.

815
00:55:54,380 --> 00:55:56,159
[SPEAKER_00] One mogu biti možda malo

816
00:55:56,500 --> 00:55:57,780
[SPEAKER_00] uobičajena, jel?

817
00:55:57,780 --> 00:55:59,400
[SPEAKER_00] I često ljudi kažu,

818
00:55:59,400 --> 00:56:01,559
[SPEAKER_00] joj, to me nikad nije pitao niko

819
00:56:01,559 --> 00:56:03,679
[SPEAKER_00] ili joj, nikad nisam razmišljao o tom.

820
00:56:03,679 --> 00:56:06,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, baš o tom treba razmišljati.

821
00:56:06,780 --> 00:56:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, kada imamo takav jedan,

822
00:56:09,079 --> 00:56:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo reći,

823
00:56:10,039 --> 00:56:11,659
[SPEAKER_00] takvu jednu nepravilnost,

824
00:56:11,659 --> 00:56:13,820
[SPEAKER_00] da naše tijelo

825
00:56:13,820 --> 00:56:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] nam ne poručuje

826
00:56:15,559 --> 00:56:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] one osnovne stvari za život,

827
00:56:17,659 --> 00:56:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] jer hrana je život,

